IN 1MM CADMIUM, WERE COMBINED TO DETERMINE THE
INTEGRAL USING EQUATIONS DERIVED IN JNE 22 759.

BOTH COMPONENTS. RANDOM ERRORS ARE GIVEN AS THE
STANDARD ERROR ON THE SPREAD OF SEVERAL MEASURMENTS
ALL RANDOM ERRORS ARE GIVEN AS 99PERCENT CONFIDENCE
LIMITS ( 3 SIGMA ) THUS THE TOTAL ERROR IS
.RANDOM ERROR AT THE 99 PERCENT CONFIDENCE LIMIT
